Slackware Current Repository by Conraid

======================================================================

mongo-c-driver (A client library written in C for MongoDB)

The MongoDB C Driver, also known as “libmongoc”, is the official
client library for C applications, and provides a base for MongoDB
drivers in higher-level languages.

HOME: https://www.mongodb.org/display/DOCS/C+Language+Center

======================================================================
REQUIRES: snappy 

